my_data <- spanish %>%
  select(., x = X14460gll, y = X14473gll) %>%
  filter(., y < 0.06, x < 0.075) 

my_data %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = x, y = y)) +
    geom_point() +
      geom_smooth(method = 'lm')

new_data <- spanish %>%
  select(., x = X14459gll, y = X14462gll) %>%
  filter(., y < 0.06, x < 0.075)

new_data %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = x, y = y)) +
    geom_point() +
    geom_smooth(method = 'lm')

#select data, filter outliers.
new_fit <- lm(y ~ x, data = new_data)
